  "屌你老母"(diú leí loú moú),is a very vulgar expression of anger, almost express insult to another person all the time.It seems literally as"fuck your mother",but its meaning can be more accurate translated to"fuck you",not to "fuck your mother".This phrase can be transformed in to various shapes depending on the name of human body parts(usually ralated to sex intercourse) in Cantonese slangs.